            . I am a pawnbroker, of Whitechapel: I have a sheet, shirt, and handkerchief, pawned by Moseley for 7s., and a tea-spoon, for 1s. 6d., in the name of Mary Gorby.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-124-person1296">
