                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker, and have a tablecloth, pawned by Moseley.</p>
               <p>MOSELEY's Defence. The things I took to Sparey's I had bought for her. I had pawned the other articles for Mrs. Gardiner, who was a very drunken woman, and lived on brandy, rum and gin, all the time I was there.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-124-person1297">
